<li id="cite_note-20"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Škend_Gumānīg_Wizār#cite_ref-20">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Mary Boyce, <i>ZRBP</i> (1979, 1985) at 155: The author relates that preparatory to writing his book he "set out to compare the teachings of Zoroastrianism with those of other faiths... ."</span>
