<li id="cite_note-80"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Škend_Gumānīg_Wizār#cite_ref-80">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">E. W. West (SBE 24) at 230 (SGV XV: 17). "Who apart from that woman saw the angel Gabriel? And on what account is it expedient to consider that woman truthful?" (SGV XV: 9).</span>
