<li id="cite_note-90"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Škend_Gumānīg_Wizār#cite_ref-90">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">E. W. West (SBE 24): St. Paul at 237 (SGV XV: 91, 93-96). For the Christian text per Mardan-Farrukh's quotation of St. Paul, West footnotes <a href="Epistle_to_the_Romans" title="Epistle to the Romans">Romans</a> vii, 19, 20, 23. For the "innermost recesses of the body", E. W. West (SBE 24) at 163 (SGV IX: 5-8)</span>
