<li id="cite_note-93"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Škend_Gumānīg_Wizār#cite_ref-93">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">The author of SGV seems to refrain from naming <a href="Jesus" title="Jesus">Jesus</a> of Nazareth, preferring to write "the Messiah".</span>
