<li id="cite_note-94"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Škend_Gumānīg_Wizār#cite_ref-94">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">E. W. West (SBE 24) at 241 (SGV XV: 134), and at 242 (SGV XV: 144-145). West footnotes <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gospel_of_Matthew" title="Gospel of Matthew">Matthew</a> vii, 17, 18, and <a href="Gospel_of_Luke" title="Gospel of Luke">Luke</a> vi, 44.</span>
