<li id="cite_note-96"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Škend_Gumānīg_Wizār#cite_ref-96">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">E. W. West (SBE 24) at 243 (SGV XVI).</span>
